sigma_analysis_results.rule_title: Suspicious Binaries and Scripts in Public Folder
sigma_analysis_results.rule_description: Detects the creation of a file with a suspicious extension in the public folder, which could indicate potential malicious activity.

sigma_analysis_results.rule_title: New RUN Key Pointing to Suspicious Folder
sigma_analysis_results.rule_description: Detects suspicious new RUN key element pointing to an executable in a suspicious folder
sigma_analysis_results.rule_author: Florian Roth (Nextron Systems), Markus Neis, Sander Wiebing

sigma_analysis_results.rule_title: Potential Defense Evasion Via Rename Of Highly Relevant Binaries
sigma_analysis_results.rule_description: Detects the execution of a renamed binary often used by attackers or malware leveraging new Sysmon OriginalFileName datapoint.
sigma_analysis_results.rule_author: Matthew Green - @mgreen27, Florian Roth (Nextron Systems), frack113

sigma_analysis_results.rule_description: Detects execution of "rundll32.exe" with a parent process of Explorer.exe. This has been observed by variants of Raspberry Robin, as first reported by Red Canary.
Detects modification of autostart extensibility point (ASEP) in registry.
sigma_analysis_results.rule_author: Victor Sergeev, Daniil Yugoslavskiy, Gleb Sukhodolskiy, Timur Zinniatullin, oscd.community, Tim Shelton, frack113 (split)

sigma_analysis_results.rule_title: Rundll32 Execution With Uncommon DLL Extension
sigma_analysis_results.rule_description: Detects the execution of rundll32 with a command line that doesn't contain a common extension
sigma_analysis_results.rule_author: Tim Shelton, Florian Roth (Nextron Systems), Yassine Oukessou

signature_matches.name: reference absolute stream path on Windows
signature_matches.rule_src:
rule:
  meta:
    name: reference absolute stream path on Windows
    namespace: host-interaction/file-system
    authors:
      - blas.kojusner@mandiant.com
      - william.ballenthin@mandiant.com
    scope: basic block
    references:
      - https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/windows/win32/fileio/file-streams
    examples:
      - 51828683DC26BFABD3994494099AE97D:0x11A9
  features:
    - and:
      - string: /^(..\?\\)?([\w]\:|\\)(\\+((?![\<\>\"\/\|\*\?\:\\])[\x20-\x5B\x5D-\x7E])+)+(\:\$?([a-zA-Z0-9_]+))?/
        # ^(..\?\\)? -> Check for path starting with "\\?\"
        # ([\w]\:|\\) -> Check for absolute path beginning
        # (\\+((?![\<\>\"\/\|\*\?\:\\])[\x20-\x5B\x5D-\x7E])+)+ -> Check for valid path and filename
        #   \\+ -> Check for at least one backslash path separator
        #   (?![\<\>\"\/\|\*\?\:\\]) -> path component must not start with <, >, ", ...
        #   [\x20-\x5B\x5D-\x7E] -> path component must be printable ASCII, except backslash path separator
        # : -> Check for start of stream filename
        # \$?([a-zA-Z0-9_]+))? -> Check for valid stream filename
        ### Example Matches:
        ### \\\\server\share\\file:stream
        ### \\\\server\share\dir.ext\\file.ext:stream 
        ### \\\\server\share\dir.ext\\file.tar.gz:stream
        ### \\\\server\share\dir.ext\\file:stream.tar.gz
        ### \\\\server\share\dir\\file.ext:stream.ext
        ### \\\\?\C:\dir1\dir2\\file:stream
        ### C:\dir\\file:stream.ext
        ### C:\dir\\file:}{+,.';[]-=-0987654321`~!@#$%^&()_+-.ext

signature_matches.name: persist via Run registry key
signature_matches.rule_src:
rule:
  meta:
    name: persist via Run registry key
    namespace: persistence/registry/run
    authors:
      - moritz.raabe@mandiant.com
    scope: function
    att&ck:
      - Persistence::Boot or Logon Autostart Execution::Registry Run Keys / Startup Folder [T1547.001]
    mbc:
      - Persistence::Registry Run Keys / Startup Folder [F0012]
    examples:
      - Practical Malware Analysis Lab 06-03.exe_:0x401130
      - b87e9dd18a5533a09d3e48a7a1efbcf6:0x1400070E0
      - 9ff8e68343cc29c1036650fc153e69f7:0x470624
  features:
    - and:
      - or:
        - match: set registry value
        - number: 0x80000001 = HKEY_CURRENT_USER
        - number: 0x80000002 = HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE
      - or:
        - and:
          - string: /Software\\Microsoft\\Windows\\CurrentVersion/i
          - or:
            - string: /Run/i
            - string: /Explorer\\Shell Folders/i
            - string: /User Shell Folders/i
            - string: /RunServices/i
            - string: /Policies\\Explorer\\Run/i
        - string: /Software\\Microsoft\\Windows NT\\CurrentVersion\\Windows\\load/i
        - string: /System\\CurrentControlSet\\Control\\Session Manager\\BootExecute/i
